translated: Jonsson, Karl Gustaf Alfred, constable, Jönköping, born April 3, 1891 in Jönköping. Married in 1921 to Anna Strahi. Employment history: graduated from trade institute in 1909, chamberlain at Jönköping-Gripenberg's railway from 1915-1918, office assistant at Västergötland-Gothenburg's railway from 1918-1919, assistant to the director of economics at Gothenburg city hospital from 1919-1920, constable at the epidemic hospital in Jönköping county and the Kindstingeitis care center in Jönköping for chrom. sick people from 1922. Church sexton in Jönköping from 1920-1932, member of the poor relief board from 1925-1936. ProPatrGM.
